Endesa Buys EDP’s Stakes in Brazil’s Ampla Electricity Companies

-- B y   J i m   S i l v e r
-- 
2011-08-05T01:10:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-05/endesa-buys-edp-s-stakes-in-brazil-s-ampla-electricity-companies.html
Endesa SA (ELE)  agreed to buy EDP-Energias
de Portugal SA’s stakes in two Brazilian power companies for a
combined 85 million euros ($120 million), EDP said.  EDP agreed to sell its 7.7 percent stakes in Ampla
Investimentos & Servicos SA and Ampla Energia & Servicos SA,
which have direct and indirect stakes in electricity
distributors, the Lisbon-based company said in a regulatory
statement last night.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jim Silver at 
 jsilver@bloomberg.net  